                        h2 Endless Luxury and Fun at Paradise: A Stay at Dreams Los Cabos Suites Golf Resort & Spa
                        h3 A Brief Overview and Beachfront Location
                        p Located along the shimmering Sea of Cortez on Mexico’s Baja California Sur Tourist Corridor, Dreams Los Cabos Suites Golf Resort & Spa is an all-inclusive resort that combines beautiful ocean views with spacious suites and a lively atmosphere perfect for families, couples, and groups. The resort sits on a long stretch of white sandy beach at Carretera Transpeninsular Km 18.5, about a 25-minute drive from Los Cabos International Airport and only minutes from both San José del Cabo and Cabo San Lucas.
                        p Designed with comfortable elegance and a vibrant tropical feel, the property offers easy access to the coast, dazzling pools, and endless activities against a backdrop of striking Baja scenery. Its prime location means guests can enjoy both resort relaxation and local excursions throughout the region.
        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 Highlights & Why It’s a Great Choice
                        p All-Inclusive Unlimited Luxury Experience
                        p The resort operates an all-inclusive program that covers gourmet dining, premium beverages, nonstop activities, pool and beach service, nightly entertainment, and more — all without the need for wristbands or extra fees.
                        p Diverse Dining & Drinks Options
                        p Guests can enjoy multiple restaurants and bars on-site, from relaxed beach grills and casual lounges to upscale a la carte venues serving international cuisine and fresh seafood. Top-shelf spirits and refreshing cocktails are included as part of the experience.
                        P Pools, Beach, and Outdoor Fun
                        p With several impressive swimming pools — including a main infinity pool, kids’ pool with water slide, and an adults-only pool with swim-up bar — plus direct access to a scenic beach, there’s plenty of space to relax or be active in the sun.
                        p Activities for All Ages
                        p Whether you’re traveling with family or friends, the resort offers a wide range of entertainment, including golf at nearby courses, tennis, beach volleyball, spa classes, dance lessons, themed nights, live music, and games.
                        p Family-Friendly Amenities
                        p Kids and teens have their own spaces and programs with the Explorer’s Club for Kids, filled with fun activities like splash parks, climbing walls, and beach games — giving parents a chance to unwind while kids stay engaged.
                        p Wellness & Relaxation
                        p The full-service spa offers a tranquil escape with a variety of treatments, hydrotherapy areas, and beachfront massage options, ideal for rejuvenation after a day of sun and activities.
                        p Elegant Suites with Ocean Views
                        p Comfortable and well-appointed suites feature private balconies or terraces — many with sea views — along with thoughtful amenities designed for relaxation and enjoyment throughout your stay.

